\pard\keepn\nowidctlpar\s2\sb120\sa120\sl240\slmult0\tx0\lang2052\kerning32\i\f1\fs28 Component Class Overview\par
\pard\li720\lang1049\kerning0\b\i0\f3\fs20 SpecificationReview\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120\lang1033 This class is a container for information about a single specification review. It holds Review and Scorecard instances. It is a simple JavaBean (POJO) that provides getters and setters for all private attributes and performs no argument validation in the setters.\par
\pard\li720\b SpecificationReviewService [interface]\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120 This interface represents a specification review service. It provides methods for scheduling specification review, submitting specification as a file or a string, retrieving specification review, retrieving specification review status and retrieving IDs of projects for which specification review positions are open.\par
\pard\li720\b SpecificationReviewServiceBean\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120 This class is an EJB that implements SpecificationReviewService business interface. This bean uses Logging Wrapper component to log all occurred errors. This class uses pluggable implementations of UploadManager, UploadExternalServices, ProjectServices, ReviewManager, ScorecardManager and ResourceManager interfaces to access data in persistence and perform the actual specification review management.\par
\pard\li720\b SpecificationReviewServiceLocal [interface]\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120 This interface represents the local interface for SpecificationReviewService session bean. It extends that interface and provides no additional methods.\par
\pard\li720\b SpecificationReviewServiceRemote [interface]\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120 This interface represents the remote interface for SpecificationReviewService session bean. It extends that interface and provides no additional methods.\par
\pard\li720\b SpecificationReviewStatus [enum]\b0\par
\pard\li1440\sa120 This is an enumeration for specification review statuses.\par
